WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:03.000
Eight points: tires, forks, chains, horn, lights,

00:03.000 --> 00:06.000
hydraulics, leaks, data plate.

00:06.000 --> 00:10.000
Tires: check for wear, damage, proper inflation.

00:10.000 --> 00:14.000
Forks: look for cracks, bends, or excessive wear.

00:14.000 --> 00:18.000
Lift chains: inspect for stretching or damaged links.

00:18.000 --> 00:22.000
Horn and lights: test all safety systems.

00:22.000 --> 00:26.000
Hydraulics: check fluid levels and connections.

00:26.000 --> 00:30.000
Look for any leaks under the truck.

00:30.000 --> 00:34.000
Data plate: must be readable and attached.
